Justification for Mapping: contents of $u would be a url leading to information about custodial history of an item, but RDA only permits a structured description (quoted string) for this property.
Transformation Notes:
Give URL as a quoted string. Append after the end of the text string from subfield a, prior to subfield $3 in this pattern: 
additional information at: [contents of $u]
Notes (Uncategorized):
Note, this would be a separate mapping from $a if there is one.
